# EarnZio — Complete App Architecture & Code Guide

## 📱 App Overview
Social media + coin rewards platform built with Flutter + Firebase.

---

## 🗂️ Firebase Database Structure (Firestore)

```
/users/{userId}
  ├── uid: string
  ├── email: string
  ├── username: string
  ├── photoUrl: string
  ├── bio: string
  ├── coins: number (default: 0)
  ├── postsToday: number (resets daily)
  ├── lastPostDate: timestamp
  ├── followers: number
  ├── following: number
  └── createdAt: timestamp

/posts/{postId}
  ├── userId: string
  ├── username: string
  ├── userPhotoUrl: string
  ├── imageUrl: string
  ├── caption: string
  ├── likesCount: number
  ├── commentsCount: number
  ├── createdAt: timestamp
  └── likes: [userId, ...]  ← for spam prevention

/posts/{postId}/comments/{commentId}
  ├── userId: string
  ├── username: string
  ├── text: string
  └── createdAt: timestamp

/notifications/{userId}/items/{notifId}
  ├── type: "like" | "comment" | "follow"
  ├── fromUser: string
  ├── message: string
  ├── coinsEarned: number
  ├── read: boolean
  └── createdAt: timestamp

/follows/{followerId_followingId}
  ├── followerId: string
  ├── followingId: string
  └── createdAt: timestamp

/leaderboard (auto-updated via Cloud Function)
  └── [sorted by coins descending]
```

