## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Firebase Setup
```bash
# Install Firebase CLI
npm install -g firebase-tools
firebase login
firebase init

# Enable: Firestore, Storage, Auth, Functions
```

### 2. Flutter Setup
```bash
flutter create earnzio
cd earnzio
# Add dependencies to pubspec.yaml (listed above)
flutter pub get

# Add google-services.json (Android) & GoogleService-Info.plist (iOS)
# from Firebase Console → Project Settings
```

### 3. Run
```bash
flutter run
```

