## 💰 Coin Reward Summary

| Action | Coins | Daily Limit |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| Upload Post | +10 | 20 posts/day |
| Get a Like | +1 | Unlimited |
| Get a Comment | +2 | Unlimited |
| Get Followed | +3 | Unlimited |
| Welcome Bonus | +50 | One-time |

---

## 🛡️ Anti-Spam / Security

- **Like spam**: `likedBy` array prevents duplicate likes per user
- **Self-like**: Blocked in CoinService (`likerId == postOwnerId`)
- **Post limit**: 20 posts/day enforced server-side
- **Daily reset**: Cloud Function resets counter at midnight
- **Auth required**: All reads/writes require Firebase Auth token
- **File size limit**: Storage rules enforce 10MB max

---

